article_title: 'Several hundred' leave Jabalia amid fighting, says Israeli military.
sentence: We  can  bring  you  an  update  now  on  the  latest  from  the  Jabalia  refugee  camp,  in  the  north  of  Gaza,  after  we  heard  earlier  that  seven  people  had  been  killed  following  an  Israeli  operation  in  the  area.
